### Contentful Delivery API - Find Parent/Reference Entities
### Based on: https://www.contentful.com/developers/docs/references/content-delivery-api/

# Your Contentful credentials
@space_id = 3p2fxa94bzao
@environment = dev
@delivery_token = xxx
@base_url = https://cdn.contentful.com
@target_entry_id = 4eVmnGmlsqO18a1Hm18H6H

### 1. Find direct parents - entries that directly reference your target entry
GET {{base_url}}/spaces/{{space_id}}/environments/{{environment}}/entries?links_to_entry={{target_entry_id}}&access_token={{delivery_token}}

### 2. Find parents of a specific content type (replace with actual content type)
GET {{base_url}}/spaces/{{space_id}}/environments/{{environment}}/entries?links_to_entry={{target_entry_id}}&content_type=REPLACE_WITH_CONTENT_TYPE&access_token={{delivery_token}}

### 3. Get all entries with full reference resolution (comprehensive but slower)
GET {{base_url}}/spaces/{{space_id}}/environments/{{environment}}/entries?include=10&access_token={{delivery_token}}

### 4. Get all locales for the space
GET {{base_url}}/spaces/{{space_id}}/environments/master/locales?access_token={{delivery_token}}
